      <h2 id="improve">Tips to Improve Your GPA</h2>
      <li class="tips">Create a study schedule and stick to it! Set aside free time to complete homework ahead of the deadlines or study for your classes. Persistence is key!</li>
      <li class="tips">Do your work well before the deadline! Do not procrastinate projects and assignments until the last minute. This will cause you stress and your performance will appear rushed.</li>
      <li class="tips">Ask for help! Talk to your teachers and your peers on confusing material and concepts. Visit a teacher at break or lunch if they are open. Silver Creek also offers bilingual tutors in the library every Tuesday and Thursday after school until 5 PM.</li>
